  "original_title": "\"\u0b95\u0bcb \u0bb9\u0bcb\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\" \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb9\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bae\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bbf \u0baa\u0bc2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe ?",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Viharamakadevi Park to hold \"Go Home Ranil\" protest without hindrance?",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "Member of Parliament Mano Ganesan mentioned on his Facebook page that President Ranil Wickramasinghe has said that Colombo Viharamakadevi Park area will be set aside for the protestors to conduct their \"Go-Home-Ranil\" protest.",
        "Ranil Wickremesinghe today held a special meeting with party leaders after being sworn in as President.",
        "Member of Parliament Mano Ganesan mentioned on his Facebook page that the President said the above.",
        "Parliament will be adjourned for 24 hours for a fresh start, President Ranil Wickremesinghe told us in a special meeting with party leaders.",
        "He also said that Colombo Viharamakadevi Park area will be set aside for the protestors to carry out their \"Go-Home-Run\" protest without any hindrance.",
        "The President also told us that he wants to bring the original 19th Amendment document of his good governance period into the Constitution as soon as possible.",
        "The recording also mentioned that the President said that he wants to form and run the government, parliament and departmental committees consisting of parliamentarians."
      ],
